---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | UtilifyGrid"
  description="Privacy policy for UtilifyGrid – free online tools. Learn how we handle your data and use of Google AdSense."
  canonicalUrl="/privacy-policy"
>
  <div style="max-width:48rem; margin:0 auto; padding:3rem 1rem;">

    <h1 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:2rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2rem;">

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Overview</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75;">
          UtilifyGrid ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website at utilifygrid.com. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Data We Collect</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
          UtilifyGrid tools run entirely in your browser. We do not collect, store, or transmit any data you enter into our tools. All calculations happen locally on your device.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75;">
          We may collect basic analytics data (pages visited, approximate location by country, device type) through privacy-friendly analytics tools to understand how our site is used and improve it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Google AdSense &amp; Cookies</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
          This site uses Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google AdSense uses cookies to serve personalised ads based on your browsing history. You can opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" style="color:#1D4ED8;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75;">
          Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits to this website and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to users based on their visit to our site and other sites on the internet.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Cloudflare</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75;">
          UtilifyGrid is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect IP addresses and request logs as part of its CDN and security services. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacy/" style="color:#1D4ED8;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a> for details.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Your Rights</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75;">
          You have the right to request access to the personal data we hold about you, and to request its deletion. Since we do not collect personal data through our tools, there is generally nothing to access or delete beyond standard server logs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Contact</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75;">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via our <a href="/contact" style="color:#1D4ED8;">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
